QuickWhatsApp
=============
version 1.0 by HA

1. Introduction
Enables user to start a conversation without saving the contact numbers.

2. Feature
2.1 Checks if the phone number entered are incomplete (i.e less than 10 digits).
2.2 Automatically add international caller id if the user forgot to put it. 
2.3 Clear the input field if any error occurs, so user can enter the correct number right away.

3. Future Planning
3.1 Include a paste function
3.2 Create a drop-down International caller id so user can select directly and let the system decide if user accidently put it in the input form
3.3 Create an option to add template messages for quicker interactions.
